{"tid":2053540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同另一半政見不合？","createTime":"2020-06-06T11:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T14:26:11.000Z","uid":107283,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e87d4f281cd5e0f31b288ca525c8555c4cc1e8ff","tid":2053540,"uid":107283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一半屋企人藍到紫 又有親戚做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我成日話佢係藍絲佢會否認，話自己係黃<br />\n但每每香港有大事發生，佢都掛住吃喝玩<br />\n記得721我地去咗日本旅行<br />\n睇完新聞我真係完全冇心情/食慾 只係想快快番香港<br />\n但佢好似唔當係一回事 仲覺得係抵打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者佢唔係藍，或者只係港豬一名<br />\n我周不時帶佢食黃店，但佢硬係會尷尷尬尬，唔識自處<br />\n久而久之都唔想逼佢陪我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔會留意邊間係藍店/紅店而叫你去食<br />\n會照食金拱門 扑野家 美心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好努力想改變佢諗法同政見<br />\n但係實際上佢比我想像中更加藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知大家一定會叫我飛撚咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地經歷好多野先一齊到，唔想咁輕易放棄呢段感情<br />\n但唔同政見真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人明？平時你地又點相處？<br />\n或者，可以話我知我應該點做？<br />\n我可以做乜改變到佢諗法？<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 呻下算<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港🇭🇰時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3828381b7e81fccf7db75951cd783618789aa7cf","tid":2053540,"uid":107283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"a94f9ebd58ea28c85d0951e6a57f2524513c09ab","tid":2053540,"uid":92255,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:05:52.000Z","msg":"其實無謂辛苦大家<br />\n價值觀唔同真係無得傾"},{"pid":"7288a24eefa234f5596fb95356f90b5f3a326023","tid":2053540,"uid":31974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"留下一個正皮支持下你<br />\n<br />\n加油 條路唔易行"},{"pid":"1437d1d1a9d9b4b4045f31d692d7ad5f8e3d0af6","tid":2053540,"uid":156468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"但佢好似唔當係一回事 仲覺得係抵打<br />\n屌你老母點忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318b7028b9f3cd06370ef1fe6690fd789e984e35","tid":2053540,"uid":289708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:08:02.000Z","msg":"佢用咩原因去話自己係黃?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a60ad5f40fecd7850c19b820338fb5ea45d919","tid":2053540,"uid":107283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a94f9ebd58ea28c85d0951e6a57f2524513c09ab","tid":2053540,"uid":92255,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:05:52.000Z","msg":"其實無謂辛苦大家<br />\n價值觀唔同真係無得傾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我唔忍心分手"},{"pid":"80f4e46d7be6d41f8e9593a6a6c02c93849305ea","tid":2053540,"uid":107283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7288a24eefa234f5596fb95356f90b5f3a326023","tid":2053540,"uid":31974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"留下一個正皮支持下你<br />\n<br />\n加油 條路唔易行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:09:00.000Z","msg":"ching過來人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b3e66712ad906ebbbde3